    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/1927">Radelchis</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, filius
                        domni bone recordationis <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/115"
                            >Adelchis</persName>, ob salute anime nostre, concessimus in <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/85"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> beate Sancte Sophie</orgName>
                        quod constructum esse dinoscitur infra hanc nostram Beneventanam civitatem,
                            <rs key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Prevosts" ref="#people/113">Crissi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Intercessory #Prevosts">prepositi</rs> supra phati cenobii <rs
                            key="#fidelisOf">fidelis</rs> nostri, integram modicam <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >terram</rs> infra eadem nostram veterem Beneventanam civitatem, que
                        pertinuit de <rs key="#Palatium #Hospitals">hospitale sacri palatii</rs>
                        nostri per hos <rs key="#Fines">fines</rs>: de duobus partibus fine terra
                        predicti monasterii Sancte Sophie, de tertia parte finem pariete ex casa
                            <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3400">monasterii
                            Sancti Benedicti quod vocatur Sinodochio</orgName>, de quarta videlicet
                        parte fine trasenda puplica predicte nostre civitatis, in ea videlicet
                        ratione ut ammodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum integram
                        supra dictam terram eodem Sancte Sofie monasterio eiusque rectores habere et
                        possidere valeas et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id est comitibus,
                        gastaldis vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam requisitionem, sed
                        perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod vero preceptum concessionis ex
                        iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName ref="#people/3466"
                            key="#Notary">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/110"
                            >Beneventum</placeName> sęcundo anno, mense februario, quinta decima
                        indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
